<plot>The subject of this Crime Does Not Pay series entry is fraudulent racetrack touts. One method they use is distributing phony tip sheets of yesterday's winners at a local track. They also "accidentally" call people who are deep in debt and leave a false tip, enticing them to make wagers they can't win.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?520114</url></doc>
